               <xd:p>semantic, publishing</xd:p>
            </xd:section> Introduction semantic publishing <xd:section
               xmlns:xd="http://www.oecd.org/ns/schema/xdocs">
               <xd:title>Definition</xd:title>
               <xd:p>28. An introduction shares an identical structural role to a chapter. However, there are
                  additional semantics. Conventionally, an introduction is considered part of the body of a
                  document in contrast to a preface or foreword, which is not.</xd:p>
            </xd:section>
         </xs:documentation>
