               <xd:title>Categories</xd:title>
               <xd:p>inline, semantic</xd:p>
            </xd:section> Phrase inline semantic <xd:section xmlns:xd="http://www.oecd.org/ns/schema/xdocs">
               <xd:title>Notes</xd:title>
               <xd:p>The semantic tags on inline content must be defined in as optional. When used they should
                  associate taxonomies with text. </xd:p>
            </xd:section> Source The semantic tags on inline content must be defined in as optional. When used
            they should associate taxonomies with text. <xd:section
               xmlns:xd="http://www.oecd.org/ns/schema/xdocs">
               <xd:title>Definition</xd:title>
               <xd:p>The semantic tag component allows a word or phrase to refer to metadata. We do not
                  envisage that metadata will be stored directly within this element – it should be stored out
